-- Croatian Konzum Sees Revenue Grow 5% This Year, Poslovni Reports
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2013-01-02T07:59:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-02/croatian-konzum-sees-revenue-grow-5-this-year-poslovni-reports.html
Konzum d.d. ,  Croatia ’s largest retail
chain, will post revenue growth of as much as 5 percent this
year on new stores,  Poslovni Dnevnik  reported on its website,
citing Darko Knez, the head of the management board.  Konzum’s revenue grew 3 percent in 2012, Knez said,
according to the Zagreb-based business newspaper. Konzum is the
retail arm of Agrokor d.d., Croatia’s largest closely-held
company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic at 
